metadata.name: Everyone's Got It. Don't Lose It.
metadata.description: What would life be like if art, design and creativity didnâ€™t play a big role in it? If we all are born with a modicum of creativity, then what forces it to erode along the road to adulthood? Fear of failure? Certain life experiences? Our schooling and authority figures? Something is causing creative corrosion. This piece is about rewarding unique insights & creative thinkers so we don't all lose that spark.
